0to%20her%20possibly%20escaping%20serving%20jail%20time%20for%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20scammer%2C%20arrested%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20was%20not%20initially%20named%20because%20she%20had%20not%20appeared%20in%20court%20yet%2C%20security%20company%20Reaction%20Unit%20South%20Africa%20(RUSA)%20said%20on%20its%20Facebook%20page%20that%20the%20woman%20is%20Prelyn%20Mohanlall%2C%20whose%20attorney%20Chris%20Gounden%20contacted%20them%20with%20the%20offer%20to%20make%20arrangements%20to%20pay%20back%20all%20victims%20that%20were%20scammed%20and%20are%20in%20possession%20of%20proof%20of%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohanlall%20allegedly%20convinced%20lovestruck%20couples%20planning%20their%20weddings%20to%20pay%20large%20sums%20in%20advance%20for%20a%20venue%20without%20having%20any%20link%20to%20the%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20couples%20arrived%20at%20the%20venue%2C%20they%20would%20find%20it%20deserted%2C%20with%20no%20water%20or%20electricity%2C%20ruining%20their%20special%20wedding%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20couples%2C%20who%20preferred%20to%20remain%20anonymous%2C%20contracted%20RUSA%20in%20December%20last%20year%20to%20track%20down%20Mohanlall.%20The%20company%20subsequently%20found%20through%20social%20media%20a%20total%20of%2017%20couples%20who%20had%20been%20scammed%20in%20this%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CComplainants%20were%20from%20several%20provinces%20in%20South%20Africa.%20A%20detective%20from%20SAPS%20Boksburg%20North%20(in%20Gauteng%20province)%20then%20contacted%20RUSA%20and%20informed%20them%20that%20the%20same%20suspect%20was%20wanted%20for%20two%20cases%20of%20fraud%20opened%20in%20Gauteng%20in%202024.%20The%20woman%20had%20defrauded%20a%20car%20dealership%20of%20R200%20000%20and%20a%20couple%20for%20R26%20000%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Head%20of%20RUSA%2C%20Prem%20Balram.%20RUSA%20said%20after%20they%20tracked%20the%20woman%20down%2C%20Mohanlall%20informed%20officers%20that%20she%20was%20a%20criminal%