20Palisades%20area%2C%20incinerating%20a%20swathe%20of%20California's%20most%20desirable%20real%20estate%20favoured%20by%20Hollywood%20celebrities.%20Gusty%20winds%20pushed%20the%20flames%2C%20pushing%20embers%20hundreds%20of%20meters%20and%20sparking%20new%20spot%20fires%20faster%20than%20firefighters%20could%20quell%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20County%20Fire%20Chief%20Anthony%20Marrone%2C%20his%20crews%20were%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20scale%20and%20speed%20of%20the%20unfolding%20disasters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20doing%20the%20very%20best%20we%20can.%20But%20no%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20enough%20fire%20personnel%20in%20LA%20County%20between%20all%20the%20departments%20to%20handle%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blaze%20raging%20in%20Pacific%20Palisades%20had%20consumed%20around%2016%2C000%20acres%20as%20of%20Wednesday%20afternoon%2C%20taking%201%2C000%20homes%20and%20businesses%20with%20it.%20A%20separate%2010%2C600-acre%20fire%20was%20burning%20around%20Altadena%2C%20north%20of%20the%20city%2C%20where%20flames%20tore%20through%20suburban%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELos%20Angeles%20County%20Sheriff%20Robert%20Luna%20said%20an%20earlier%20death%20toll%20of%20two%20had%20now%20increased%2C%20with%20more%20deaths%20feared.%20%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20it's%20grown%20to%20five%20as%20we%20continue%20through%20this%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20Luna%20told%20radio%20station%20KNX.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20remember%2C%20this%20is%20still%20a%20very%20fluid%20situation%2C%20there's%20zero%20containment%20on%20this%20fire.%20I'm%20really%20praying%20we%20don't%20find%20more%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvacuation%20orders%20were%20in%20place%20for%20about%2070%2C000%20people%20across%20the%20area.%20A%20large%20number%20of%20people%20who%20did%20not%20heed%20warnings%20to%20leave%20had%20suffered%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20injuries%2C%26quot%3B%20Marrone%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWater%20Shortage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20pall%20of%20dark%20smoke%20hung%20over%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20hydrants%20were%20drying%20as%20the%20water%20supply%20dropped%20in%20the%20area.%20Los%20Angeles%20Department%20of%20Water%20and%20Power%20chief%20executive%20Janisse%20Quinones%20pleaded%20with%20people%20to%20save%20water%20after%20hydrants%20in%20Pacific%20Palisades%20ran%20dry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20fighting%20a%20wildfire%20with%20urban%20water%20systems%2C%20and%20that%20is%20really%20challenging%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoe%20Biden%2C%20who%20was%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20with%20California%20Governor%20Gavin%20Newsom%2C%20was%20briefed%20on%20what%20the%20president%20called%20an%20%26quot%3Bastounding%26quot%3B%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20doing%20anything%20and%20everything%2C%20and%20as%20long%20as%20it%20takes%20to%20contain%20these%20fires%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHollywood%20Screeched%20To%20A%20Halt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20showbiz%20capital%20has%20been%20besieged%20by%20multiple%20out-of-control%20blazes%2C%20with%20Hollywood%20events%20including%20a%20glitzy%20awards%20show%20and%20a%20Pamela%20Anderson%20film%20premiere%20among%20those%20cancelled%20as%20firefighters%20battle%20flames%20in%20hurricane-force%20winds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20homes%20were%20destroyed%20in%20the%20swanky%20Pacific%20Palisades%20area%2C%20a%20favourite%20spot%20for%20celebrities%20where%20multimillion-dollar%20houses%20nestle%20on%20beautiful%20hillsides%2C%20while%20other%20infernos%20sprang%20up%20across%20the%20north%20of%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20boss%20Elon%20Musk%20showed%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20fire%20in%20one%20of%20the%20suburban%20areas%20in%20LA%20with%20cars%2C%20homes%20and%20trees%20compl