r-Gavaskar%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20a%20lot%20of%20great%20fast%20bowlers%2C%20Curtly%20Ambrose%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Glenn%20McGrath%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F292-glenn-mcgrath-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGlenn%20McGrath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20didn't%20get%20to%20play%20T20%20cricket%2C%20so%20I'm%20not%20talking%20about%20those%20guys%2C%20but%20in%20regards%20to%20anyone%20who%20has%20played%20all%20three%20formats%2C%20I%20think%20he%20might%20be%20the%20best%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20actually%20that%20good%20in%20any%20conditions%2C%20that's%20what%20makes%20him%20great%3B%20any%20conditions%2C%20any%20format%2C%20this%20guy's%20a%20freak.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736387820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F5q046d2o_mohammed-shami-afp_625x300_02_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Findias-champions-trophy-squad-bcci-eyeing-star-whos-been-out-of-action-for-417-days-jasprit-bumrah-uncertain-7430480%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Champions%20Trophy%20starts%20on%20February%2019%2C%20while%20India's%20first%20match%20is%20on%20February%2020%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Findias-champions-trophy-squad-bcci-eyeing-star-whos-been-out-of-action-for-417-days-jasprit-bumrah-uncertain-7430480%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20military%20finds%20body%20of%20a%20hostage%20in%20Gaza%2C%20examining%20identity%20of%20the%202nd%20one%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736387668000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117068946%2Cimgsize-1626217.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisraeli-military-finds-bod