l%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fport-strike-dockworkers-union-automation-job-replacement-concerns-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternational%20Longshoremen's%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20US%20Maritime%20Alliance%20said%20Wednesday%20they%20had%20agreed%20on%20a%20new%20six-year%20master%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sides%20said%20in%20a%20joint%20statement%20that%20this%20will%20allow%20them%20to%20avoid%20any%20work%20stoppages%20on%20January%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20agreement%20protects%20current%20ILA%20jobs%20and%20establishes%20a%20framework%20for%20implementing%20technologies%20that%20will%20create%20more%20jobs%20while%20modernizing%20East%20and%20Gulf%20coast%20ports%20%E2%80%94%20making%20them%20safer%20and%20more%20efficient%2C%20and%20creating%20the%20capacity%20they%20need%20to%20keep%20our%20supply%20chains%20strong%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20joint%20statement%20read%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20deal%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bwin-win%20agreement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ILA%20and%20USMX%20said%20they%20would%20get%20their%20members%20to%20review%20and%20approve%20the%20agreement%20before%20it%20is%20released%20publicly.%20For%20now%2C%20both%20sides%20will%20continue%20to%20operate%20under%20their%20current%20contract%20until%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20new%20agreement%20are%20ratified%20via%20a%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdockworkers-port-strike-ila-impacts-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrike%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20have%20potentially%20paralyzed%20shipping%20lines%20along%20the%20East%20and%20Gulf%20Coasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDetails%20of%20the%20agreement%20were%20not%20made%20public%2C%20but%20the%20joint%20statement%20said%20dockworkers%20received%20some%20protections%20against%20having%20their%20jobs%20replaced%20by%20automation%2C%20which%20was%20one%20of%20the%20union's%20key%20concern