0the%20street%20throwing%20things%20in%20their%20cars%20and%20driving%20off.%20It%20was%20terrifying.%20I%20grabbed%20our%20dog%20Gus%20and%20just%20as%20I%20was%20leaving%2C%20my%20neighbor%20across%20the%20street%20called%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20pick%20up%20her%20dog%20since%20she%20wasn't%20home.%20I%20went%20back%20into%20my%20house%2C%20got%20her%20key%2C%20and%20put%20her%20dog%20in%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smoke%20from%20the%20LA%20wildfire%20covered%20the%20sky%20of%20the%20Palisades%20community%20in%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677efe6a8951662c9f1f5412%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmoke%20descended%20upon%20the%20neighborhood.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20courtesy%20of%20Alisa%20Wolfson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20friend%20whose%20daughter%20goes%20to%20the%20same%20school%20as%20mine%20picked%20our%20girls%20up%2C%20and%20we%20met%20at%20her%20house%2C%20which%20was%20just%20outside%20the%20evacuation%20zone.%20We%20put%20all%20the%20dogs%20in%20the%20yard%2C%20and%20the%20girls%20played%20with%20their%20friends.%20I%20thought%20we'd%20just%20camp%20out%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20but%20then%20things%20started%20to%20look%20terrible%20really%20quickly.%20Around%201%20p.m.%2C%20my%20husband%20borrowed%20our%20friend's%20e-bike%20and%20rode%20to%20our%20house%20to%20see%20if%20there%20was%20anything%20he%20could%20do%20and%20to%20grab%20a%20few%20things%20left%20behind.%20He%20saw%20tons%20of%20smoke%2C%20firemen%2C%20and%20the%20hillsides%20burning%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20really%20wild.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20stayed%20at%20our%20friend's%20house%20until%20they%20lost%20power%2C%20then%20checked%20into%20the%20Beverly%20Hilton.%20It%20was%20like%20all%20of%20West%20Los%20Angeles%20had%20descended%20upon%20the%20hotel%20%E2%80%94%20it%20took%2040%20minutes%20just%20to%20pull%20into%20