four-bedroom%20unit%20at%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20apartment%20complex%2C%20Common%20Elmwood%2C%20where%20Jerrid%20Powell%20had%20already%20been%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPowell%2C%2034%2C%20was%20arrested%20and%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fda.lacounty.gov%2Fmedia%2Fnews%2Fman-charged-killings-four-including-three-la-unhoused-people%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20charged%3C%2Fa%3E%20later%20that%20year%20with%20four%20counts%20of%20murder%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20shooting%20deaths%20of%20three%20sleeping%20homeless%20men%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20the%20fatal%20shooting%20of%20another%20man%20at%20a%20home%20in%20California's%20San%20Dimas.%20Prosecutors%20say%20the%20killings%20spanned%20a%20four-day%20period%20in%20November%202023.%20Powell%2C%20who%20remains%20held%20without%20bail%20pretrial%20at%20a%20Los%20Angeles%20jail%2C%20has%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20to%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20time%20Common%20offered%20a%20lease%20to%20Mr.%20Castagna%2C%20Common%20was%20already%20aware%20that%20Mr.%20Powell%20had%20exhibited%20abnormal%20and%20alarming%20behavior%20and%20had%20not%20paid%20his%20rent%20for%20over%20a%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Common%20and%20attorneys%20for%20Powell%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e73ce470-e315-4201-8ba1-865714a7b78b%5C%22%3ECastagna%20alleges%20months%20of%20living%20in%20fear%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECastagna%20said%20in%20his%20lawsuit%20that%20during%20his%20roughly%20three%20months%20of%20living%20with%20Powell%2C%20his%20roommate%20displayed%20%26quot%3Berratic%20behavior%2C%26quot%3B%20repeatedly%20made%20threats%2C%20including%20one%20to%20%26quot%3Bslap%20the%20shit%20out%20of%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20stole%20his%20food.%20The%20lawsuit%20also%20alleges%20the%20torture%20of%20a%20dog%20inside%20the%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20which%20only%20names%20Common%20as%20a%20defendant%2C%20Castagna%20accuses%20the%20company%20of%20negligence%20and%20a%20breach%20of%20warranty%20of%20habitability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCommon%20made%20absolutely%20no%20effort%20to%20try%20to%20investigate%20the%20complaints%2C%20to%20do%20any%20sort%20of%20safety%20assessment%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20attorney%20for%20Castagna%2C%20Carrie%20Goldberg%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20Brooklyn-based%20law%20firm%20C.A.%20Goldberg%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECastagna%20said%20in%20the%20suit%20that%20Common%20forced%20him%20to%20%26quot%3Bendure%20an%20untenable%20and%20unsafe%20living%20situation%20that%20continued%20to%20escalate%20in%20severity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20move-in%20day%2C%20Powell%20%26quot%3Bforcefully%20asserted%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20owned%20Common%20and%20later%20claimed%20he%20owned%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnike-new-ceo-elliott-hill-change-sport-sales-wholesalers-turnaround-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Nike%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbmw-ceo-2035-gasoline-vehicle-ban-eu-more-reliant-china-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBMW%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20suit%20said.%20Powell%20also%20claimed%20to%20be%20God%2C%20Castagna%20alleges%20in%20the%20lawsuit.%20With%20shards%20of%20glass%20scattered%20around%20the%20floor%2C%20it%20appeared%20that%20a%20mirror%20had%20been%20punched%2C%20shattering%20it%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20note%20was%20later%20posted%20on%20the%20apartment's%20front%20door%20stating%20that%20Powell%20owed%20nearly%20%2418%2C000%20in%20back%20rent%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bef9aac4-39eb-49fb-a5c6-eed19e74396e%5C%22%3ECommon%20tried%20to%20profit%20from%20Castagna's%20desperation%2C%20lawsuit%20said%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20moving%20in%2C%20Castagna%20began%20contacting%20Common%20to%20raise%20his%20concerns%20about%20his%20living%20situation%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%20He%20contacted%20the%20company%20for%20help%20on%20how%20to%20proceed%20with%20his%20%26quot%3Bseemingly%20unstable%20and%20unpredictable%20roommate%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20received%20no%20response%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20week%20of%20moving%20in%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said%20Castagna%20contacted%20Common%20a%20second%20time%2C%20explaining%20that%20he%20felt%20unsafe%20within%20the%20apartment%2C%20but%20no%20one%20responded%20to%20him%20until%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20email%20to%20Common%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said%20Castagna%20reported%20that%20Powell%20was%20playing%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20loud%20and%20disruptive%26quot%3B%20YouTube%20videos%20of%20goats%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night.%20Castagna%20said%20in%20the%20suit%20that%20when%20he%20asked%20Powell%20to%20lower%20the%20volume%2C%20Powell%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20you%20going%20to%20do%20about%20it%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECastagna%20said%20in%20the%20email%20that%20he%20feared%20for%20his%20physical%20wellbeing%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20repeated%20emails%20from%20Castagna%20asking%20to%20transfer%20units%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said%20Common%20eventually%20told%20him%20there%20would%20be%20an%20up-to-%24500%20transfer%20fee%20and%20an%20additional%20security%20deposit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECastagna%20had%20moved%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20for%20a%20new%20job%20at%20a%20biosafety%20lab%20in%20a%20children's%20hospital%20and%20did%20not%20have%20disposable%20money%20to%20pay%20additional%20fees%20or%20a%20higher%20rent%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20treated%20the%20situation%20as%20%26quot%3Bnonurgent%26quot%3B%20and%20told%20Castagna%20there%20would%20be%20a%2030-day%20waiting%20period%20before%20a%20transfer%20would%20be%20possible%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20states%20that%20Powell%20%26quot%3Bbecame%20increasingly%20menacing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2287c27b3d-ace9-4e09-9cf7-e79a2266ab7e%5C%22%3ELAPD%20called%20after%20'piercing%20sounds%20of%20animal%20distress'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2024%2C%202023%20%E2%80%94%20just%20days%20before%20Powell's%20arrest%20%E2%80%94%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20Castagna%20overheard%20%26quot%3Bpiercing%20sounds%20of%20animal%20distress%26quot%3B%20coming%20from%20Powell's%20bedroom%2C%20prompting%20Castagna%20to%20call%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Police%20Department.%20LAPD%20records%20obtained%20by%20BI%20show%20that%20a%20911%20call%20was%20made%20on%20that%20date%20to%20the%20Common%20Elmwood%20complex%20for%20a%20report%20of%20animal%20cruelty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20said%20the%20LAPD%20knocked%20on%20the%20apartment%20door%2C%20which%20Powell%20answered%2C%20and%20police%20could%20not%20gain%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Castagna%20later%20saw%20an%20injured%20dog%20in%20the%20common%20area%20of%20the%20apartment%20with%20a%20prolapsed%20anus%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20said%20Castagna%20contacted%20Common%20about%20the%20matter%2C%20and%20Common%20emailed%20Castagna%20the%20following%20week%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20allegations%20about%20Jerrid's%20treatment%20of%20the%20dog%20are%20false.%20There%20is%20no%20further%20action%20for%20our%20team%20to%20take.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPowell%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20killings%20on%20November%2030%2C%202023%2C%20about%20six%20months%20before%20Common%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20said%20that%20it%20was%20not%20until%20LAPD%20officers%20broke%20through%20the%20apartment%20door%20on%20the%20day%20of%20Powell's%20arrest%20and%20briefly%20handcuffed%20Castagna%20%26quot%3Bsimply%20because%20he%20was%20living%20in%20the%20same%20apartment%20as%20an%2