20of%20the%20law%2C%20but%20in%20terms%20of%20learning%20basic%20values%2C%20the%20ethical%20values%2C%20which%20are%20associated%20with%20life.%20That%20generation%20of%20judges%20and%20lawyers%20was%20very%20strong%20in%20their%20foundational%20principles%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Chandrachud%20said%20his%20father%20let%20him%20choose%20his%20own%20career%20path%20and%20set%20an%20example%20by%20making%20time%20for%20his%20family%20and%20never%20imposing%20his%20view%20on%20them.%20In%20their%20later%20years%2C%20he%20said%2C%20his%20father%20was%20more%20of%20a%20friend%20to%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20when%20the%20call%20of%20higher%20judicial%20office%20came%20to%20me%20-%20I%20was%20asked%20to%20become%20a%20judge%20when%20I%20was%20just%2038%20years%20old%20-%20and%20my%20appointment%20was%20not%20coming%20through%20for%20two%20years%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20well%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20get%20on%20with%20the%20law%20and%20be%20a%20lawyer%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life.%20And%20when%20I%20looked%20at%20him%20(my%20father)%20for%20advice%2C%20he%20said%2C%20do%20as%20you%20please%2C%20and%20I'll%20support%20you%20in%20whatever%20you%20do.%20Perhaps%2C%20he%20said%2C%20you%20will%20do%20equally%20satisfying%20work%20and%20fulfilling%20law%20work%20as%20a%20lawyer%20at%20the%20bar%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20also%20said%20he%20had%20the%20good%20fortune%20of%20seeing%20some%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bgreats%20of%20the%20bar%26quot%3B%20at%20work%20and%20also%20working%20with%20some%20of%20them.%20He%20said%20he%20learnt%20a%20lot%20from%20Fali%20Nariman%2C%20Soli%20Sorabjee%20and%20K%20Parasaran.%20He%20also%20praised%20former%20Solicitor%20General%20KK%20Venugopal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHarvard%20Degree%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Chandrachud%20said%20he%20learnt%20a%20policy%20oriented%20approach%20to%20law%20at%20Harvard%20Law%20School%20and%20also%20got%20educated%20in%20policy%20as%20a%20student%20of%20Economics%20at%20Delhi%20University%20and%20at%20the%20Campus%20Law%20Centre%20in%20Delhi.%20Professor%20Lotika%20Sarkar%2C%20he%20said%2C%20gave%20students%20like%20him%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20groundings%26quot%3B%20in%20feminist%20jurisprudence%20when%20people%20were%20not%20talking%20about%20feminism%20in%20law%20in%20the%201980s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20spoke%20about%20how%20the%20Harvard%20Law%20degree%20did%20not%20have%20much%20of%20an%20impact%20immediately%20after%20he%20returned%20to%20practice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20realised%20this%20to%20my%20disappointment%20when%20I%20got%20my%20first%20brief%20as%20a%20young%20lawyer%20in%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court.%20I%20had%20an%20SJD%20from%20Harvard%20Law%20School%2C%20which%20is%20a%20Doctorate%20in%20Juridical%20Science%2C%20and%20my%20first%20brief%20was%20a%20little%20docket%20to%20mention%20before%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court.%20I%20asked%20the%20solicitor%3A%20'How%20much%20do%20I%20mark%20on%20the%20docket%2C%20what%20is%20my%20fee%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFees%20in%20Bombay%20in%20those%20days%20were%20marked%20in%20GMs%2C%20which%20is%20gold%20mohurs%2C%20and%20one%20GM%20was%2015%20rupees.%20So%20the%20solicitor%20looked%20at%20me%20and%20said%2C%20'You%20know%2C%20for%20this%20particular%20work%2C%20the%20ordinary%20fee%20would%20be%20five%20GMs%2C%20which%20would%20be%2075%20rupees.%20But%20since%20you%20are%20first%20appearing%20before%20the%20high%20court%2C%20I%20will%20give%20you%20six%20guineas%20for%20this%20case.%20So%20I%20realised%20that%2C%20notwithstanding%20a%20Harvard%20PhD%2C%20what%20I%20could%20mark%20in%20those%20days%20was%20about%2075%20rupees%20or%2090%20rupees%20in%20the%20mid-eighties%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20life%20teaches%20you%20so%20many%20good%20lessons%2C%20you%20know%3F%20And%20you%20realise%20that%20a%20good%20academic%20degree%20is%20important%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20everything%20in%20itself%20when%20you%20actually%20join%20the%20profession.%20But%20Harvard%20benefited%20me%20as%20time%20went%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHumility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20what%20was%20one%20his%20most%20important%20judgments%2C%20the%20scrapping%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20as%20a%20means%20of%20political%20funding%2C%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said%20a%20judge%20applies%20intellectual%20rigour%20and%20the%20basic%20principles%20of%20law%20to%20arrive%20at%20a%20verdict.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20instance%2C%20when%20you%20decide%20a%20case%20like%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case%2C%20when%20it%20opens%2C%20you%20are%20conscious%20of%20the%20ramifications%20of%20what%20you%20are%20deciding%20and%20you%20are%20conscious%20of%20the%20impact%20which%20the%20case%20will%20have%20on%20the%20polity%20in%20the%20long%20run%20-%20it%20is%20obviously%20something%20which%20is%20present%20to%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20court.%20But%20when%20you%20arere%20deciding%20the%20case%20in%20terms%20of%20intellectual%20rigour%2C%20you%20are%20applying%20the%20basic%20principles%20which%20are%20associated%20with%20that%20body%20of%20law.%20So%2C%20in%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case%2C%20we%20were%20applying%20fundamental%20principles%20of%20manifest%20arbitrariness%20or%20the%20need%20for%20transparency%20in%20electoral%20funding%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Chandrachud%20said%20judges%20are%20conscious%20that%20what%20they%20are%20deciding%20now%20will%20impact%20society%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20constantly%20reminds%20you%2C%20as%20a%20judge%2C%20to%20be%20humble.%20Humility%20is%20something%20you%20learn%20as%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20because%20you%20are%20conscious%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20field%20of%20knowledge%20is%20so%20vast%2C%20and%20it's%20far%20vaster%20than%20any%20of%20us%20as%20judges%20or%20lawyers%20can%20fathom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736360160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F9cg6jdig_dy-chandrachud_625x300_08_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flaw-was-not-my-first-choice-ex-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-to-ndtv-7430548%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20law%20was%20not%20the%20first%20choice%20and%20he%20almost%20pursued%20a%20post-graduate%20degree%20in%20Economics%20instead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flaw-was-not-my-first-choice-ex-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-to-ndtv-7430548%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20least%206%20killled%2C%20several%20injured%20in%20stampede%20at%20Tirupati%20temple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736359829000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fat-least-6-killled-several-injured-in-stampede-at-tirupati-temple-125010801318_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20devotees%2C%20including%20three%20women%20died%20and%20several%20more%20were%20injured%20in%20a%20stampede%20here%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20as%20hundreds%20of%20them%20jostled%20for%20tickets%20for%20Vaikunta%20Dwara%20Darshanam%20at%20Lord%20Venkateswara%20Swamy%20temple%20on%20Tirumala%20Hills%2C%20a%20police%20official%20...%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fat-least-6-killled-several-injured-in-stampede-at-tirupati-temple-125010801318_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3