%20gold%20mohurs%20(GM).%20And%2C%20you%20know%2C%20one%20gold%20mohur%20was%20Rs%2015.%20I%20believe%20the%20Calcutta%20GM%20was%20Rs%2016.%20So%20the%20solicitor%20looked%20at%20me%20and%20said%2C%20you%20know%2C%20for%20this%20particular%20work%20which%20you%20are%20doing%20in%20the%20court%20for%20me%2C%20the%20ordinary%20fee%20would%20be%20five%20GMs%2C%20which%20would%20be%20Rs%2075.%20But%20since%20you%20are%20first%20appearing%20before%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20I%20will%20give%20you%20six%20guineas%20for%20this%20case.%20So%20I%20realised%20that%20notwithstanding%20a%20Harvard%20PhD%2C%20what%20I%20could%20mark%20in%20those%20days%20was%20about%20Rs%2075%20rupees%20Rs%2090%20in%20the%20mid-eighties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETackling%20various%20cases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20would%20think%20that%20no%20judgment%20which%20a%20judge%20delivers%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20is%20easy%20in%20itself.%20Because%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20speaks%2C%20it%20speaks%20for%20the%20future.%20It%20speaks%20for%20the%20present%2C%20and%20it%20speaks%20for%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20always%20had%20this%20confidence%20in%20the%20High%20Court%20that%20there%20was%20a%20court%20above%20us%20to%20correct%20a%20possible%20error.%20In%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20great%20challenges%20that%20you%20know%20that%20you%20speak%20as%20a%20final%20court%20of%20appeal%2C%20there's%20no%20court%20higher%20than%20you.%20And%2C%20therefore%2C%20there%20is%20no%20case%20which%20I%20feel%20in%20that%20sense%20for%20us%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20is%20an%20easy%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETask%20of%20delivering%20judgments%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20judges%2C%20you%20are%20conscious%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20what%20you%20are%20deciding%20now%20will%20impact%20our%20society...%20When%20arguments%20close%2C%20that's%20the%20time%20for%20reflection%20for%20a%20judge%20when%20you're%20really%20left%20with%20yourself.%20When%20a%20case%20is%20concluded%20in%20terms%20of%20arguments%20and%2C%20you%20know%2C%20you%20reserve%20a%20case%20for%20judgment%2C%20that's%20when%20the%20real%20process%20of%20judging%20starts%20because%20then%20you%20are%20just%20left%20to%20yourself.%20There%20is%20no%20one%20else%20with%20you%20but%20your%20papers.%20So%2C%20you%20know%2C%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20judging%20itself%20is%20a%20very%20lonely%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERuling%20on%20electoral%20bonds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20decide%20a%20case%20like%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case%2C%20when%20it%20opens%2C%20you%20are%20conscious%20of%20the%20ramifications%20of%20what%20you%20are%20deciding%20and%20you%20are%20conscious%20of%20the%20impact%20which%20the%20case%20will%20have%20on%20the%20polity%20in%20the%20long%20run%20-%20it%20is%20obviously%20something%20which%20is%20present%20to%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20court.%20But%20when%20you%20are%20deciding%20the%20case%20in%20terms%20of%20intellectual%20rigour%2C%20you%20are%20applying%20the%20basic%20principles%20which%20are%20associated%20with%20that%20body%20of%20law.%20So%2C%20in%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case%2C%20we%20were%20applying%20fundamental%20principles%20of%20manifest%20arbitrariness%20or%20the%20need%20for%20transparency%20in%20electoral%20funding.%3Cbr%3E%5CnOverruling%20previous%20top%20court%20judgments%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20say%20that%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20final%20not%20because%20it%20is%20right%2C%20but%20it%20is%20right%20because%20it%20is%20final.%20And%2C%20you%20know%2C%20that%20is%20why%20we%2C%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20have%20looked%20at%20the%20correctness%20of%20some%20of%20the%20past%20judgments%20which%20were%20delivered.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%202024%2C%20and%20even%20earlier%2C%20we%20overruled%20several%20judgments%20which%20were%20delivered%20by%20our%20predecessors%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%201970s%2C%201980s%20and%20the%201990s.%20And%20we%20overruled%20those%20judgments%20not%20necessarily%20because%20they%20were%20wrong.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20those%20judgments%20may%20have%20had%20some%20bearing%20on%20the%20society%20in%20which%20they%20were%20delivered%2C%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20context%20in%20which%20they%20were%20delivered.%20But%20those%20judgments%20did%20not%20make%20sense%20today%20as%20society%20has%20evolved...%20I%20overruled%20a%20couple%20of%20judgments%20delivered%20by%20my%20own%20father.%20And%2C%20but%20that's%20part%20of%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECriticisms%20of%20courts%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20age%20of%20social%20media%2C%20everything%20that%20is%20said%20in%20court%20now%20becomes%20a%20part%20of%20a%20public%20dialogue%20in%20the%20process%20of%20dissection.%20Our%20attention%20spans%20are%20so%20limited%20today%2C%20down%20to%2020%20seconds%2C%20on%20social%20media%20that%20people%20don't%20understand%20the%20distinction%20between%20a%20dialogue%20in%20a%20court%20and%20the%20final%20judgment%20of%20the%20court.%20Even%20before%20the%20final%20judgment%20of%20a%20court%20comes%2C%20people%20feel%20that%20the%20dialogue%20is%20reflective%20of%20your%20position%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20quite%20right.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20criticism%20of%20a%20judge%2C%20the%20targeting%20of%20a%20judge%20is%20based%20not%20on%20any%20concrete%20material%2C%20but%20just%20what%20anybody%20can%20say%20about%20a%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECourtroom%20scenes%20in%20films%20vs%20reality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bollywood%20scenes%20about%20courts%20are%20very%20different%20from%20what%20actually%20happens%20in%20reality%20in%20the%20court.%20Yes%2C%20there%20is%20drama%2C%20and%20at%20times%2C%20there%20is%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20drama%2C%20particularly%20in%20sensitive%20cases.%20But%20a%20lot%20of%20times%2C%20what%20goes%20on%20in%20court%20is%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20you%20know%2C%20bare%20bone%20exposition%20of%20facts%20and%20law.%20So%20it's%20very%20different%20from%20how%20the%20court%20is%20portrayed%20in%20Bollywood%20films%20of%20that%20matter%20and%20some%20of%20the%20Hollywood%20films%20as%20well%20or%20other%20films%20of%20a%20different%20genre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcompletely-unfounded-ex-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-on-criticisms-over-supreme-court-vacations-7429928%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupreme%20Court%20vacations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20criticism%20that%20the%20court%20has%20too%20many%20vacations%20is%20completely%20unfounded%20because%20it%20doesn't%2C%20you%20know.%20It's%20not%20justified%20by%20what%20is%20the%20truth%2C%20which%20is%2C%20the%20judges%20are%20working%2024*7%2C%20365%20days.%20The%20first%20victim%20of%20a%20life%20on%20the%20bench%20is%20your%20own%20ability%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20your%20own%20family.%20So%20I%20am%20making%20up%20for%20lost%20ground%20now%2C%20you%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736359320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fj72autso_dy-chandrachud_625x300_08_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffrom-first-fee-to-films-on-court-drama-what-former-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-told-ndtv-interview-7430497%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20spoke%20to%20NDTV%20on%20a%20range%20of%20issues%20pertaining%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffrom-first-fee-to-films-on-court-drama-what-former-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-told-ndtv-interview-7430497%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indices%20end%20with%20minor%2