istan.%20This%20included%20priority%20assistance%20in%20the%20healthcare%20sector%2C%20supply%20of%20medicines%2C%20and%20rehabilitation%20of%20refugees.%20New%20Delhi%20has%20so%20far%20dispatched%20several%20shipments%20consisting%20of%2050%2C000%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20wheat%2C%20300%20tonnes%20of%20medicines%2C%2027%20tonnes%20of%20earthquake%20relief%20aid%2C%2040%2C000%20litres%20of%20pesticides%2C%20100%20million%20polio%20doses%2C%201.5%20million%20doses%20of%20the%20Covid%20vaccine%2C%2011%2C000%20units%20of%20hygiene%20kits%20for%20the%20drug%20de-addiction%20programme%2C%20500%20units%20of%20winter%20clothing%20and%201.2%20tonnes%20of%20stationery%20kits%2C%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Afghan%20Minister%20appreciated%20and%20thanked%20the%20Indian%20leadership%20for%20continuing%20to%20engage%20and%20support%20the%20people%20of%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fdaqig02c_vikram-misri-afghan-foreign-minister-mawlawi-amir-khan-muttaqi_625x300_08_January_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20has%20also%20conveyed%20to%20Kabul%20its%20readiness%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20urgent%20developmental%20needs%20of%20the%20Afghan%20people.%20%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20the%20current%20need%20for%20development%20activities%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20India%20would%20consider%20engaging%20in%20development%20projects%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20talks%20progressed%2C%20Afghanistan's%20foreign%20minister%20underlined%20Kabul's%20sensitivities%20to%20India's%20regional%20security%20concerns%20and%20assured%20full%20cooperation%20in%20this%20regard.%20According%20to%20a%20press%20statement%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20also%20agreed%20to%20promote%20the%20use%20of%20Chabahar%20port%20for%20supporting%20trade%20and%20commercial%20activities%2C%20including%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20humanitarian%20assistance%20for%20Afghanistan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Misri%20also%20underscored%20the%20importance%20India%20gives%20to%20its%20historic%2C%20civilisational%2C%20and%20cultural%20ties%20with%20Afghanistan.%20%26quot%3BThe%20foreign%20secretary%20underlined%20India's%20historic%20friendship%20with%20the%20Afghan%20people%20and%20the%20strong%20people-to-people%20contacts%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EForeign%20Secy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVikramMisri%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40VikramMisri%3C%2Fa%3E%20met%20Acting%20Foreign%20Minister%20of%20Afghanistan%20Mawlawi%20Amir%20Khan%20Muttaqi%20in%20Dubai%20today.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnBoth%20sides%20discussed%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3's%20ongoing%20humanitarian%20assistance%20to%20Afghanistan%2C%20bilateral%20issues%20and%20security%20situation%20in%20the%20region.%20India%20reiterated%20its%20commitment%20to%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fa3UyuIqkAG%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fa3UyuIqkAG%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20(%40MEAIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMEAIndia%2Fstatus%2F1876979447175217450%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%208%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESports%2C%20especially%20cricket%2C%20which%20is%20loved%20in%20both%20countries%20also%20figured%20in%20the%20talks.%20Both%20sides%20agreed%20to%20strengthen%20sporting%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWednesday's%20meeting%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20comes%20two%20days%20after%20New%20Delhi%20severely%20condemned%20the%20recent%20Pakistani%20airstrikes%20in%20Afghanistan%20that%20killed%2046%20people%2C%20including%20several%20women%20and%20children.%20The%20Pakistani%20air%20strikes%20were%20carried%20out%20on%20December%2024.%20It%20invited%20massive%20criticism%20and%20a%20stern%20warning%20from%20the%20Afghan%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistani%20air%20strikes%20hit%20Barmal%20district%20in%20Afghanistan's%20Paktika%20province.%20This%20was%20the%20second%20time%20in%202024%20that%20Islamabad%20directly%20targeted%20%26quot%3Bcivilian%20areas%26quot%3B%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20said%20the%20government%20in%20Kabul.%20In%20March%202024%20too%2C%20a%20similar%20air%20strike%20by%20Pakistan%20had%20killed%20eight%20people%2C%20including%20three%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20India%20strongly%20condemned%20Pakistan%20over%20the%20air%20strikes%2C%20saying%20it%20is%20Islamabad's%20%26quot%3Bold%20practice%26quot%3B%20to%20blame%20its%20neighbours%20for%20its%20failures%20within%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20noted%20the%20media%20reports%20on%20airstrikes%20on%20Afghan%20civilians%2C%20including%20women%20and%20children%2C%20in%20which%20several%20precious%20lives%20have%20been%20lost.%20We%20unequivocally%20condemn%20any%20attack%20on%20innocent%20civilians.%20It%20is%20an%20old%20practice%20of%20Pakistan%20to%20blame%20its%20neighbours%20for%20its%20own%20internal%20failures.%20We%20have%20also%20noted%20the%20response%20of%20an%20Afghan%20spokesperson%20in%20this%20regard%2C%26quot%3B%20India's%20foreign%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Taliban%2C%20a%20predominantly%20Pashtun%20tribe%20which%20has%20a%20large%20presence%20across%20Afghanistan%2C%20is%20an%20ultra-conservative%20political%20and%20religious%20hardliner%20group.%20It%20refers%20to%20itself%20by%20its%20state%20name%2C%20the%20Islamic%20Emirate%20of%20Afghanistan.%20The%20Taliban%20which%20was%20the%20government%20in%20Afghanistan%20in%201996%2C%20was%20overthrown%20by%20the%20US-led%20military%20coalition%20in%202001%20after%20Washington%20launched%20its%20'war%20against%20terror'%20focusing%20on%20the%20Al%20Qaeda%20and%20Osama%20bin%20Laden.%20Twenty%20years%20later%2C%20in%202021%2C%20when%20the%20US%20military%20left%20Afghanistan%20abruptly%2C%20the%20Afghan%20Taliban%20swept%20across%20the%20nation%20and%20regained%20its%20political%20importance%20by%20forming%20the%20government%20in%20the%20war-torn%20country.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736356920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F0n74dcio_vikram-misri-afghan-foreign-minister-mawlawi-amir-khan-muttaqi_625x300_08_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-afghan-taliban-government-hold-top-meet-in-dubai-discuss-chabahar-port-7430326%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20high-level%20meeting%20between%20the%20Afghan%20Taliban%20leadership%20and%20senior%20Indian%20officials%20was%20organised%20is%20Dubai%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-afghan-taliban-government-hold-top-meet-in-dubai-discuss-chabahar-port-7430326%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Body%20found%20in%20search%20for%20missing%20British%20hikers%20in%20northern%20Italy%20believed%20to%20be%20Samuel%20Harris%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736356680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F01%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-samuel-harris-missing_6793669.jpg%3F20250107155721%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbody-found-in-search-for-missing-british-hikers-in-northern-italy-believed-to-be-samuel-harris-13285601%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20charity%20that%20one%20of%20the%20British%20hikers%20missing%20in%20northern%20Italy%20works%20for%20has%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Baware%20of%20reports%20the%20body%20of%20Sam%20Harris%20has%20been%20recovered%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engage