.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-390996%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENoori%20holds%20over%2022%20leadership%20positions%20and%20possesses%20strong%20oratory%20and%20logical%20skills.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20outreach%20worker%2C%20Noori%20started%20conducting%20meetings%20for%20people%20affected%20by%20HIV.%20It%20was%20during%20one%20of%20these%20meetings%20that%20she%20met%20Dr%20Joseph%20Williams%2C%20the%20then-director%20of%20VHS%20Hospital.%20Together%2C%20they%20established%20the%20South%20India%20Positive%20Network%2C%20an%20NGO%20for%20which%20Noori%20was%20elected%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDr%20Williams%20was%20instrumental%20in%20this%20endeavour%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Noori.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20did%20he%20guide%20us%20through%20the%20registration%20process%20but%20also%20provided%20crucial%20support%20in%20setting%20up%20the%20organisation.%20I%20consider%20him%20a%20trusted%20mentor%20even%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20for%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20State%20AIDS%20Control%20Society%2C%20Noori%20submitted%20a%20proposal%20to%20aid%20HIV%20positive%20individuals%2C%20written%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20Dr%20Williams.%20She%20was%20able%20to%20secure%20the%20project%20to%20provide%20support%20and%20care%2C%20worth%20Rs%203.12%20lakh%20for%20their%20upliftment%2C%20and%20she%20executed%20the%20same%20skillfully%20with%20just%20three%20staff%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20worked%20on%20over%2010%20projects%20and%20I%20was%20promoted%20to%20a%20position%20where%20I%20could%20recruit%20more%20than%2070%20staff.%20I%20have%20good%20oratory%20skills%20which%20have%20created%20an%20impact%20among%2