s.%20It%20was%20Reena%2C%20her%20house%20help%20at%20the%20time%2C%20who%20stepped%20in.%20She%20suggested%20where%20they%20could%20find%20the%20necessary%20materials%20and%20mentioned%20that%20she%20had%20some%20basic%20stitching%20skills%20that%20could%20come%20in%20handy.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20we%20worked%20together%2C%20and%20the%20very%20first%20batch%20of%20collars%20that%20we%20made%2C%20we%20made%20with%20her%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rimjhim%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReena%20Dhanak%2C%2035%2C%20from%20a%20small%20settlement%20near%20Indore%2C%20has%20her%20own%20unique%20journey%20in%20animal%20welfare.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20be%20honest%2C%20I%20was%20always%20against%20having%20dogs%20loitering%20outside%20my%20house%20%E2%80%94%20not%20because%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20them%2C%20but%20because%20I%20was%20scared%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241208-WA0127-1733988839-500x889.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Pawsitivity%20worker%20gently%20pets%20a%20dog%20proudly%20wearing%20one%20of%20the%20reflective%20collars%20she%20helped%20create.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241208-WA0127-1733988839-500x889.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241208-WA0127-1733988839-169x300.jpg%20169w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241208-WA0127-1733988839-150x267.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241208-WA0127-1733988839.jpg%20631w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388999%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22889%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPawsitivity%E2%80%99s%20reflective%20collars%20help%20preven