0NGOs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%E2%80%99s%20group%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai%20relies%20heavily%20on%20these%20collars%2C%20as%20they%20are%20a%20lifesaver%20on%20highways.%20%E2%80%9CWithout%20them%2C%20many%20dogs%20would%20be%20invisible%20to%20drivers%2C%20and%20accidents%20are%20inevitable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEducating%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20the%20animal%20welfare%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETushar%20Shende%20(39)%2C%20Rimjhim%E2%80%99s%20husband%2C%20has%20been%20a%20crucial%20part%20of%20the%20Pawsitivity%20journey%2C%20handling%20the%20administrative%20and%20operational%20aspects%20of%20the%20venture%20along%20with%20his%20own%20job.%20Tushar%2C%20who%20was%20once%20terrified%20of%20dogs%2C%20now%20understands%20their%20needs%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20spreading%20awareness%20about%20responsible%20feeding%20and%20animal%20interaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20they%20both%20have%20been%20conducting%20school%20awareness%20programmes%20to%20teach%20children%20how%20to%20safely%20approach%20stray%20dogs%20and%20behave%20around%20them.%20%E2%80%9CA%20lack%20of%20understanding%20can%20lead%20to%20either%20the%20children%20hurting%20the%20animal%20or%20getting%20hurt%20themselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tushar%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20teach%20children%20how%20to%20safely%20and%20respectfully%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F379789%2Fkind-hour-foundation-mouli-mehrotra-lucknow-art-education-animal-welfare-compassion-community%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einteract%20with%20animals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20creating%20positive%20experiences%20for%20both%20the%20animals%20and%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20programmes%20are%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20Pawsitivity%E2%80%99s%20mission%2C%20ensuring%20that%20children%20g