sing%20on%20human%20rights.%20We%20were%20inspired%20to%20take%20up%20initiatives%20that%20boost%20the%20income%20of%20rural%20residents.%E2%80%9D%20Besides%20her%20role%20in%20the%20association%2C%20Anusuya%20also%20works%20as%20a%20translator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20innovative%20approach%20not%20only%20addresses%20the%20waste%20problem%20but%20also%20generates%20additional%20income%20for%20farmers.%20Currently%2C%20at%20least%201%2C000%20farmers%20across%20Kordha%2C%20Cuttack%2C%20and%20Puri%20districts%20of%20Odisha%20are%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20approach%20provides%20a%20valuable%20template%20for%20rural%20development%20and%20demonstrates%20the%20potential%20of%20waste-to-wealth%20initiatives%20in%20promoting%20sustainable%20agricultural%20practices%20and%20improving%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20rural%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kasinath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20every%20stem%2C%20we%20give%20Rs%2070-80%20to%20a%20farmer.%20By%20collecting%20waste%20from%20farm%20sites%2C%20we%20clean%20their%20field.%20This%20indirectly%20helps%20them%20as%20it%20saves%20them%20labour%20costs.%20On%20average%2C%20a%20farmer%20associated%20with%20us%20earns%20an%20additional%20Rs%207%2C000%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20for%20banana%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%E2%80%99s%20impact%20extends%20beyond%20the%20economic%20realm.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20removing%20banana%20waste%20from%20the%20fields%2C%20this%20approach%20contributes%20to%20a%20cleaner%20environment.%20The%20elimination%20of%20open%20burning%20prevents%20air%20pollution%20and%20mitigates%20the%20risk%20of%20soil%20contamination%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Kasinath%2C%20this%20work%20is%20purely%20selfless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20association%20of%20farmers.%20Around%2040%20people%20are%20employed%20here%20to%20handle%20the%20processing%20work%2C%20and%20they%20earn%20a%20salary%20from%20the%20profits.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20any%20share%20of%20the%20earnings%20%E2%80%94%20I%20sustain%20myself%20through%20my%20consultancy%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20way%20of%20contributing%20to%20the%20betterment%20of%20society%20and%20supporting%20my%20farmer%20brothers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Kasinath%20Jena%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735620427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fbanana-waste-4-1734954508.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D391779%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Khordha%20district%2C%20Anusuya%20and%20Kasinath%20Jena%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Jayadev%20Banana%20Farmers%20and%20Artisans%20Association%E2%80%99%20upcycles%20post-harvest%20banana%20waste%20into%20various%20products%2C%20providing%20an%20additional%20income%20source%20for%201%2C000%20farmers%20while%20promoting%20zero-waste%20farming%20practices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F391779%2Fodisha-kasinath-anasuya-jena-jayadev-banana-farmers-upcycle-post-harvest-waste%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221%20Year%2C%20Countless%20Smiles%3A%20How%20YOU%20Helped%20%E2%80%98The%20Better%20India%E2%80%99%20Make%20a%20Difference%20in%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20you%20helped%201%2C000%20children%20from%20farming%20families%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20hinterlands%20receive%20school%20kits%3B%20ensured%206%2C000%20labourers%20in%20Mirzapur%20got%20a%20pair%20of%20slippers%2C%20and%20brought%20joy%20to%20hundreds%20of%20children%20by%20giving%20their%20school%20a%20new%20roof.%20Yes%2C%20you%20did%20it!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20impact%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20every%